          "reviewBody": "This school has been very developed since 2023 it is a very nice school. The school is beneficial for average students it gives importance to sports. The average or below-average students participate in one or the other activities which they have the talent to perform. The thing is the food in the cafeteria is so expensive and also they don't have the appropriate lunch to fill student's tummies. I give this school a -1 star because of a teacher who doesn't even like tall people because she is so short and her name is Saranya mam(soc sci) always insults students for getting low marks (above just pass) in art education, not even a main subject. I don't know how many like that mam.",
